Package com.google.common.css

Class JobDescriptionBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.css.JobDescriptionBuilder
  • public class JobDescriptionBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Aids in the creation of inputs for the compiler. A builder can be used for creating a single JobDescription.
